            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%2316%E5%B2%81%E7%94%B7%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%9F%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%E7%9C%8B%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%83%85%23&amp;extparam=%2316%E5%B2%81%E7%94%B7%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%9F%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%E7%9C%8B%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%83%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#16岁男高中生医院看包皮父母表示不知情#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】这天，16岁男高中生在朋友陪同下来到深圳市儿童医院急诊外科，因翻包皮后未复位导致阴茎肿胀，隔了一天才来看诊，医生检查后震惊不已“你不怕坏死啊！”。复位后医生表示要致电孩子父亲，孩子直言好尴尬！面对医生的询问孩子父亲尴尬地支支吾吾，表示孩子没和他们说过，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%AE%A9%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E5%AF%B9%E5%84%BF%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E9%9A%BE%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%AE%A9%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E5%AF%B9%E5%84%BF%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E9%9A%BE%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#是什么让爸爸对儿子的性教育难开口#</span></a>&nbsp;？小卫提醒：性教育是孩子成长中的必修课，父母可不能忽视呀！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#闪闪的儿科医生#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4901693956227113" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster=