            <description><![CDATA[【今天母亲节，说些情话给妈妈<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[爱你]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_aini-09d5f3f870.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】“我觉得妈妈很忙，她是卫生监督警察。”有这样一群人，他们工作在卫生监督的一线，他们既是父母，也是儿女。今天他们想说些情话给自己的母亲。岁月在妈妈身上留下痕迹，皱纹攀爬上她的脸庞，鬓角平添了许多银发，可在我的记忆中，她一直是我小时候二三十岁的模样……一起来听听👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%AF%8D%E4%BA%B2%E8%8A%82%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%AF%8D%E4%BA%B2%E8%8A%82%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#母亲节#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A6%88%E5%A6%88%E6%88%91%E5%BE%88%E7%88%B1%E4%BD%A0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#妈妈我很爱你#</span></a> （深圳卫生监督） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4901248441450561" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫生监督的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/ac97bb04gy1hdxpv1nm3tj225q17qnpe.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/ImXojqzagx085qxgiGOQ01041201iOWu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684157549&amp;ssig=j2zQTdT6si&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/FHWwXAUIgx085qxeNGFi01041200EW420E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684157549&amp;ssig=ukNVTsSsxv&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/5R1ZZ6Oqgx085qxewro401041200pDAf0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684157549&amp;ssig=yPtEK8Rjju&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A490